extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em Bike Inventory]

  h1 Inventory Items

  if error
    p Error getting Inventory Items.
  else
    p The inventory has the following counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Bikes:] !{data.bike_count}
      li #[strong Manufacturers:] !{data.manufacturer_count}
      li #[strong Types:] !{data.type_count}
